{"questionId":"11875","questionHtml":"<p>Explain where the condition <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n \\geqslant 2\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mo>⩾</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span> was used in your proof.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>need <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n \\geqslant 2\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mo>⩾</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;so that the powers of tan in&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} {{\\text{ta}}{{\\text{n}}^{n - 2}}} x\\,{\\text{se}}{{\\text{c}}^2}x\\,dx - \\int\\limits_0^{\\tfrac{\\pi }{4}} {{\\text{ta}}{{\\text{n}}^{n - 2}}} x\\,dx\">\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtext>ta</mtext>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mrow>\n          <mtext>n</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>n</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </msup>\n    </mrow>\n  </mrow>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>se</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>c</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>d</mi>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mfrac>\n          <mi>π</mi>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n        </mfrac>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtext>ta</mtext>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <msup>\n        <mrow>\n          <mtext>n</mtext>\n        </mrow